O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ na yo ni pan mbo,“Mbe kro ni tnihaa wa,mbra yirɛ le dumm,imi na mɛŋɛ woni blee,brɛmm ndram wrɛmu,na yirɛ kun nyjila kre.Ndee imi na lafo yila,weerii brɛmm kre.”
A O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ na yo mbo, “Imi na ni sumifun Isaiah tro wejiwaara, mu nyaari jewaara yɛlɛ taarɛ kre, ki pe sɛmbɛɛrɛ kee na nyina kee sisaa ŋga kie Egypt, na Cush leele da.
E na nyumu le haa kpɔɔ ka pe,kakpɔɔ kre na,mbe nyumu na fuu mbra yilii,tapla lɛɛ kre nu,mbra paan mbra lee ki nu.La, e nsra Nyiɛkpɔɔ le mu nya,wre wra yire kee nyjɛ jawa,mu tɛɛ fa na yie pe.
Na yɛlɛ fuloe taarɛ na kɛ yire waa tro, o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ we ti mbe Tyre ndru mbe ki jafa lɛɛ kre li na. Pan chia kre we pe na chlɔ ŋmba u uyɛ prɛ mu leele ŋga waŋgra kro nu tra yiɛ na wi.
Kre nyua ŋga na we fooro yonyi,nyjɛ yi waŋgrɛ kro leele tɔ,yire laala mbe wa.
La, na ni leele pre loŋgoolo,pre chaa mbe ni kɛ tɔ pe na,kena pe pan mbe mi,na pre tni wejinyiŋge nu.”
Nyiɛkpɔɔ KachindɛE ndie tɛɛ,e kee ŋga ni yuu ŋga loo,e kee ŋga ni yuu,e pan ŋga dɔɔ ta chichie.
Nyu Nunu Waara PeeO Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ paara mbo,“Judah ŋulo atɛ, ŋgi na hin?Pe yiri mu ni taan.Jawala nyjɛ yi n yiri ni pan,na pe taa.Mu na nyu nunu nyjɛ yi n tna,ni pan pini na leele ni,na sisam pini na yaa sisam na.
Nyjila ŋga nu o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ we na Assyria leele pre gbuun kre, na u leele pree wa na binyi, na juru gbuun. Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre titi we wi na Assyria leele pre ni.
NyiɛtalaaŊu waŋgra ŋga ndro,ŋmba u ni leele klai, u atɛ,kii wa na ndro n da mu ŋu kla tun,la, mu atɛ.Ndro n da mu mu wɔ mu ŋga tun,la, ŋu mi leele wɔ mu ŋga, mu atɛ.Na maa ni leele klaa,na pe wɔŋgaa ti, pie mu kla,mbe mu wɔ mbe ŋgambe fɔlɔ tɔ.
Zion ndra na,o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ ble wɔ mu tɛɛ,mbe pe loŋgoolo sisam fɔlɔ tɔ.
A ŋunɔwifɛɛnlɛ lopom wre na kna mbo, “E jawa na yire, na ŋunu wre chiin pan waŋgra lopom wre ni tun na yire kee nyjɛ ni ree? Pan ma, leele mblɛ pe tni mboo ŋga na ŋga, pe chaa. Yire na pre kro we e yɛ fre ka, mbe e yɛ fnimi gbɔ.”
Isaiah Kee Ŋga Wra Yo Ŋunu Wre PanA Isaiah na tia pra sɛ yo Ŋunu Hezekiah pan na, “Kee ŋga o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ, Israel Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre yo yi kre mbo, ‘Ŋga mu yire Assyria ŋunu Sennacherib mandiɛ na mu ni tali kre ndra na.
Ni mana na kan,a ndaa nyɛni na katoo kotro wi.Ndaa yiɛ yire mu le nyjeeri chiin,a ni nyiɛlɛ na fna.O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ ni fnai,kena jande ya ni na.
Kpra na,pan waŋgrɛ leele pre nyi,na nyumu ŋga ki mu bokiti nu yi,o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre pan.A pan pe nyi na bloŋgo yiu pan.A pan koyɔɔsu nyjɛ haa yi le,yire snamu pe u panna bloŋgo yi.
E le, ee pe na,yirɛ tre yira fɔŋgɔ,ŋga ŋgaala yi nɛɛ,a yi nyu tna,a pra yirɛ trei na yi ni.Ee nyuɛ, na nyambie tre,mbe yi juari mbruru,mbe yi pe na yirɛ fue yi.
La, leele mblɛ pe peyɛ wru,mu taa sɛɛnlɛ na,mu yirɛ nyjɛ lewo gbeele,wru mu na sumi kre,pie ndru kro,mbe sɛ na nyifɛɛrɛ kpɔɔ ni.”
E n pan mbaala ni,mbe yurɛ sroo sra wɔmbe ni ŋga,a e n srawɔɔ tɛɛmu ni le yɛnyiŋge.Ni n e tɔɔra na e shɔlɔ,ndee tuwe ndiom tɛɛn tɛɛ,mbe sra wɔ mbe ni ŋga.
La, mi ni tia,ni kee nyanyofɛɛnlɛ kee,nyjɛ pe yo mu tɛɛyire na pini kpra.Pe yuu na leele we ndru,mbe Jerusalem nyi na,a pie ndru,mbe Judah chiɛ yire gbeele,mbe sin mbe yia pe kajɛɛ na,a mbe ti mbe yi pe ma yɛŋgɛ.
Hali mbe sɛ su e lɛlɛm,na e ndra fniŋge nyjila.Mi wi e Nyiɛkpɔɔ ŋmba mbe e le.Mi ndaa e wa,a mbe e yii nyjila kro nu.A mbe ya e na, mbe e shɔ.
Fuŋgaami ni yire kee yire pe,ŋga ni yi pe ki n mu,e n da mu yi loo tun,ki tia ndro wa jaa yo na,‘Ni yire kee yire chin.’
Jerusalem, ni mu mɛɛ nyunɔ,ni kandala,ki tia mba jaa mu kee fɛɛ.
A ŋu ma mna tia epo na yua,a mna tia kolo na sni ki nu,mna tia leele mblɛ ndra,mna lɔ pre na tro kree?
Ndro nsra u le mu nya,a pra u je,U kee naa fooro ni,a wra kala nya mu mu.Leele naa u le na yiɛ woni u na,pe nsra u le mu nya,a ndro nsra u ŋga buuro.
E le, ee waŋgrɛ,nyjɛ leele e n chin,a pe n e chin pre yeeri,a tafɛŋgɛ ni pie pan.Ŋgi na hin? E Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ,Israel Nyiɛkpɔɔ Cheche wre,we e le kre yɛnyiŋge ŋga.”
Yirɛ nyji yirɛ yi sɛɛnlɛ,a e na yi fiɛ,mu tia e na kala fnɛ ni pan,mu ni kee fɛɛ ma ŋga hin?Kena ŋga ni pieri mu e ti,a ki mu kre, kre ki tia,e n na ni kaan buuro ŋgaa?
E pini nyaanyaa mbe sɛ sisaa pe,ndee mbe sɛ ndro,ŋmba u n yaka pe cha, mbe gbo.A lawee ŋga nu ee tro kpan,ee bawa ja, mbe ki kla.
Ŋga mbe paan mu ŋga,swafre kre, mbe ki ti,mbe paan mu ŋga swanyiɛ.Ŋga mbe paan mu ŋga,tɔɔnrɔ kre,mbe paan mu ŋga swafiŋge.A ŋga mbe mu ŋga,nyuŋgo kɛɛn kre,mbe paan mu ŋga swafre.A na mbe paan mu ŋga dnɛ kre,tɔɔnrɔ mbe paan mu ŋga.Mbe ti mbe mu lefɛɛnlɛ pre mu le,wejinyiŋge na frakaa ni.
O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre ki nyu wɔ mbo,“Mi nunu ni waŋgrɛ yire taanla,na tre sɛnyi yi simi fɛɛri ndoo wa,a ndro n ya ni na.Krɔkuɔn sisaa ni ni tɛɛ,mu pe taanla,a pe nyimi wo ni dodonyi na,ma kre,mu ni dodonyi manakro poŋgo.
Pre pe shie na jiin,fanyi lawee blee,mbra gboolo yeeri.Pe prako kaara kaa,a sɛɛn kaara tumu yii wa,pe chɔɛ sɔɔ wee nu.
Kena yire mblɛ,e Jerusalem kori kre,e ti mbe yire na wre yiɛshɔ.Yire mblɛ e nyɛni na u kaan kre,e ti mbe yire nawre yiɛshɔ kpɔɔ.
Kena Jeremiah, muyɛ kna, yiri mu kee ŋga ni yo mu pan kro yo pe pan. Maa shia pe fiɛ, na kre ma mbe ti mbe pe kee pe fiɛrɛ ni mu pan.
Mni a e na taanri ni na,mu yiri mu ni taan hin?Pan mi e Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔwre yo.
Ŋga o sɛ na sɛɛnlɛ yire suminyambie,na nyuɛ yire ndra na kre,o n yaka ta yi nu.Kpra na, o chin na Israel leeleNyiɛkpɔɔ wre wio ŋmaashɔfun.
Soolo nduufɛɛnlɛ,na snimi wafɛɛnlɛ gblee,we ti mbe chiɛ yire leele kro fɛ.Pe plɛ we fɛ mbe sɛ le klɔɛ nu,mbe pe plɛ fɛmbe nyuɛ dnɛ nduu.Pie fɛ mbe pe chiɛ yire kro ti,a ndro wa kro yi na.
Kena mi Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre n fna,mbe pre leele pre ndie tini ra?Kena yire waŋgra nyjɛ,yi yire kee nyjɛ pini kre,mba fɔlɔ tɔ pe na ra?
<sup>(29-30)</sup> Mu jaa swafiŋge le fnunu nu,ŋga ki wɛɛrɛ titi nu,mbe nɛɛrɛ wɔ ki nu,la, ni leele pre sisam kpɔɔ mu tro,a ndro wa jaa nɛɛrɛ laa pe na,a ki tia mi Nyiɛkpɔɔ pe je.”
O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre yo mbo, “Judah leele sisam pe ni yiɛ, pe sɛ sɛɛnlɛ nyjɛ yi pe afunyi yirɛ yire tɛɛ Suminyuŋgo ŋga na ni mɛɛ taa kre nu, mu ki tɔ na nɛɛrɛ ni.
Ndro u nunu fana,a pra kpra yo peyɛ pan.Pe n yaka chin, na kafinɛ bɔkɔ,a pia jaa sisam pee ti.
La, o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ,wre wi Nyiɛkpɔɔ titi.Wre wi Nyiɛkpɔɔ ŋmba wraa ku,a wre wi ŋunu,ŋmba uu wa nyjila kro nu.Na u krɔ kun tra we seeri,a waŋgrɛ wa jaa yire,mbe u krɔkuɔn kre shie.
O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre na yo na,pan e na nyi na Olive tiŋge,ŋga na sɛnyi chichiele nyi yi.La, kia mu mbe ni ti,mbe leŋunɔ plɛ gble le,mbe paan tiŋge kre klɛ knumumbe wo,mbe yi koli mbe sɛ le kanhun.
A ndaa sɛ Euphrates lɔɔ kre mbɛɛ na wa, mna sɛ greree kre tuu mu ki wɔ mna ndaa ki ndra kre. Ŋga ndaa ki wɔ kre na kla, kia jaa yaka pe na.
O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre na yo ni pan mbo, “Jeremiah, maa shia chichie tali mbe pre leele mblɛ ŋga.
Mbe ti mbe mu sheli na mboo,ŋga pe swafre tɛɛ mu sin yi.Leele pre we wi na mu ni,la, pia mu ja.Ŋgi na hin? Nii wa mu kro,mbe mu shɔ pe kɛɛ.Pan mi, mu TafunNyiɛkpɔɔ wre yo.”
Lewo loloŋgo pe yira,ŋga ki ndro fana,mu wɛ yira kro na,a ki chinɛɛ sheli.Lewo ŋmbi we jaaŋga kii wa ki nu chin hin?
Kena ŋga mi e Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre yuu yi na,E sɛ waŋgrɛ yire leele pre wie,na pe da mu yire kefuɛn,nyjɛ yire Israel leele pini,nyjɛ ka loo tun rɛ?
A ŋu Pashhur, na leele mblɛ pee wa mu katoo wa kro we sɛ pe tinlɛ Babylon tra nu. Bawa mu ku mbe pe mu le, ŋu na mu nɔɔlɔ mblɛ pan mu kafinɛ kee nyaa na yuu pre kro.”
La, na e je ni nyu kee na, mi e Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre ni yɛ danyi da na, kre ŋunu katoo ŋga we kla. Pan ni yo.”
Wre ŋunu wre nyjila,kre Judah tra we kiyɛ ta,mbe Israel leele tniwejinyiŋge nu.Mɛɛ ŋga ni pie nawre ŋunu wre yeeri yi,o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ,o frakafun.
Kee nyjɛ e kro na keenyanyofɛɛnlɛ pre wie yi na, “Kee ŋgi Nyiɛkpɔɔ ta mu o nyu wɔ aŋga hin? Ndee kee ŋgi u ta mu yo o pan hin?”
Ndaa sɛ Jerusalem na Judah chiɛ yire na, a pe ŋulo na pe loplombo kro na simi kre ka gbɔ, a kra tia waŋgra kre na ja, mna kaari kataa mna leele fo titi, a praa pe le na kpɔli yira ka yi, na pe suni, imi na e pe nyaa aŋga ŋga.
A srawɔfɛɛnlɛ pre, na Nyiɛkpɔɔ keenyanyofɛɛnlɛ pre na leele pre, na pe loplombo kro bɔ mandiɛ mbo, “Ki fna mbe o wre blɔ ŋmba gbo, ŋgi na hin? U paara mu o kakpɔɔ ŋga taan, a e kro ki loo.”
Na keenyanyofɛɛnlɛ lɛ yɛŋgɛ, a mi Nyiɛkpɔɔ kee pe nyaa na yuu wala, kena e ti mbe pe mi Nyiɛkpɔɔ Jaŋgafun wre tali, mbe ki ti yirɛ hɛnyi nyjɛ yi kro Suminyuŋgo wa, na Jerusalem ŋunu katoo wa yire, mbe pia ndru mbe paan yi koli mbe sɛ Babylon tra nu na.
Kee ŋga o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre yuu yi kre, na Babylon waa jaŋga li yɛlɛ fuloe taarɛ na kɛ mu kɔ kre, mbe pan e pan mbe e nyina ni dumiɛn nyu kee ŋga ndaa yo kre, a mbe ndru mbe pan na e ni mna.
Na ki pan ma,pie mi pe Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔwre na ŋunu David nana,ŋmba mbe wɔ,mbe u pe pe ŋunu wre sumi.
Kee ŋga o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre yuu u pan yi kre mbo,Maa nyɛni, muyɛ yii,mu mu yetunyi tlu,ŋgi na hin? Ŋga mu pe,mu mu biile pre ŋga kre,mu ki fɔtɔɔrɔ ta.Pie yili pe loŋgo wre tra nu,mbe ndru mbe pan.
“Mu nalɔ Shallum ŋmba biblɔ wi Hanamel wre we pan mbe yo mu pan na, sɛ ni tra ŋga kii wa Anathoth ŋga kii wa Benjamin tra nu kre lɔ, ŋu ki fna mu ki lɔ, ŋgi na hin? Ni sele ndro titi wi ŋu.”
Pie pe, ni leele, mbe ni pe, pe Nyiɛkpɔɔ na.
Pan chɔɔ mba kɔ ni nyu nunu na mbe Abraham, na Isaac, na Jacob nanae pre je, ndee mbe nyu ŋga ndaa yo pe pan na nyjila kro nu pie Ŋunu David nanae pre wa ta mbe u jɔɔn li kre kla. Ki tia mbe nyu Israel leele pre na, mbe pe ndru mbe pe tnimu lɛɛ kre ta na.”
ndee mu nyuŋgo sin mu tni ki nu, ndee mu fali mu yirɛ luu tun.
A ŋunu wre na Jehudi tun a wra sɛ hlɛ kre wru pe nyunɔfun Elishama nyuŋgo wa, mna pan mu ki tɔɔnri mu ŋunu wre nyina. Na u loplombo pre kro wa mu yire u jaara.
La, ni tafun, fuŋgaami ni mu tali mbe mu ni kee ŋga loo ni pan. Ni mu tali, maa ti pe ndruu sɛ ni le nyuŋgo wa na, na kre ma mbe ku wa.”
A Zedekiah ŋunumu lie kre yɛlɛ kɛmbɔnunu kre nyiɛpɔ jijirɛ wo kre ble ŋga kra taa kɔɔnanyjirɛ kre na, kre pra ja mu kakpɔɔ kre mboo ŋga pe sin mu ki fɛ mu kun kre juari, mna le chia kre lam.
A Kareah biblɔ Johanan wre na sɛ ju mu yo Gedaliah pan mbo, “Ti mbe ni sɛ Nethaniah biblɔ Ishmael wre gbo mbe ndro wa chin. Ŋgi ki tia wra mu chaa mbe gbo, mbe ti mbe Judah leele mblɛ pee wa mu kɛɛ ŋga fɛ mbe nyina, mbe sɛ ku ŋga hin?”
Mbe e fooro le, imi kie pe mbe u e fooro le, mbe ti e kro e waŋgra nu.
Mni a e na ni krɔ kuun na e sɛɛnlɛ nyjɛ e gbeele na sumi yire ni, mu ndru na tuwe ndiom tɛɛn sroi na Egypt sɛɛnlɛ kaan ŋga hin? Yire titi ee eyɛ kla. Mbe ti waŋgrɛ yire leele na e le na suŋgɔ leele lɛ yire.
E krafi le e soolo pre na,e pe wɔ fimi na, e tni pe na,e e ŋunɔ wi juulee,haa cha e le.E e snimi nyu liɔ,e yirɛ nyjɛ ni,e eyɛ toni ŋunɔ yire wru,e lawee cha e yire chiriri.
Mni brɔfiɛŋunu kre we pe,mbe tni mbe wuu hin?O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre,u paara mu ki ŋga tnumu,na ki wi na Ashkelon leele,mblɛ pee wa epo nyu na pre ni.
Ki tia mbe nyɛni,mbe Moab leele ŋga,mbe fooro li,mbe Kir-Hareseth leele ŋga.
Edom waŋgra,ni paan mbe mu pe fiɛn,waŋgrɛ yire kro yiɛ,mbe ndro kro mu le fiɛn.
Ŋmba we pe nya kro,we na pe kuu.A pe loŋgoolo pre we na yuu na,o n pimi li, ŋgi na hin?Pe sisaa pe,mu pe Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ taan,wre ŋmba wraa pe kaan,kahaa chichie kre,pe Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ,ŋmba na pe tolɛɛlɛnaa kaan wre,pra sisaa pe mu u taan.
Wam sisaa we yire tra kre nu,mbe pe lɔɛ kro yua.Babylon, bawa sɛɛnlɛ,nyjɛ yi leele piɛri nyi,mu tia ki leele kaari jijiele.
Ŋu ni ndaa tɛɛ mna mbaala,na pe lefɛɛnlɛ gbun,mna mu tɛɛ mu falifɛɛnlɛ,na pe nuulomblɛ ni pe fali gbun.A ŋu ni ndaa ŋulona pe loplombo gbun.
E loo, gblee ka kunBabylon haa na paan.Leele pe Babylon klai na paan,a kra tini ma kre.
Yire pilaasi yire nunu gedem naa fiiti fulo na kɔɔnashin, a nunu na pe fiiti kɛmbɔkɔɔnatarɛ mu fɛ mu kun, a ki gbidiŋge na da na kambɛlɛ ni, a pra yi lam wɔ wee.
O Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre fraka,nde ndaa je mu yirimu u nyu kee taan.Leele mblɛ ee wa lawee kro nu,e loo, e kanyana ŋga nu ni nyi le.Pe ni nyanyjɛbɛɛlɛ,na ni bichabɛɛlɛ yii,mu sɛ na pe ni waŋgra fɔŋgɔ nu.
U wii na ni ni,mu tia fooro na kanyanani fɛ mu kun.
Kena na pe ndro kala limu kpra fɛɛlɛ,o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wrewa ki chin ra?
Jerusalem Ndie TiniɛSwanyiɛ titi kla,a kia jaa chiɛnri na,pe Suminyuŋgo dnɛnyjɛ yi chiɛnri yire,yi nyina mu wo lete na.
Klo titi tia wejinyi wɛɛri o na,na kanhun pe le fnunu nu.
Na ki pan na yurɛ pre shie kre, mbe yirɛ nyjɛ yi pe sakri jeelee yire na shie na pe ni, na nyjeeri pe yiri naa, mbe pe yiri na yi ni.
A Nyiɛkpɔɔ ŋumu wre na ni yire nyjeeri, a ndaa mana kpɔɔ ka loo ni kro na ki yuu mbo, “E o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre yɛnyiŋge kre ŋga mɛɛ, u tni haa wa nyjeeri.”
A Nyiɛkpɔɔ na ndru mna yo ni pan mbo, “Ezekiel, lewo na nyjuro, mbe ti klo to Jerusalem na, kie ti mbe pe dankna kro kɔ, mbe tutom wo pe na mbe praa sro na nyumu kra mbra peyɛ kaan.
Na pe waa gboolo nya pe sragbuɛnlɛɛ yire, na nyambie yire, na nyuɛ yire, na tinyi kpɔɛ wrɛ wee nyjɛ jaara pe sɛɛnlɛ sumi na tuwe ndion tɛɛn sroi kre, kre pie chin na mi wi pe Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ.
A kra pe na kɛ u tini mu ni ndra nyjure yii, a ndaa nya na Nyiɛkpɔɔ ŋumu ni kɔ nyjeeri mna sɛ na ni ni Jerusalem na. Ŋumu wre na sɛ na ni ni Suminyuŋgo kre jlonwee lam wo ŋga kii wa na shie nyjeeri haa kre nyu na, bawa sɛɛn ka na nyi mna pe afuŋgo yira, na krɔ kun kee o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ wre pan.
Cherubim pre kuɛn naa tini kpɔɔ na o Tafun Nyiɛkpɔɔ Jaŋgafun wre mana yi, hali na mu yire Suminyuŋgo lawee vankam fimi wo kre nu, mu yi tiŋge loo.
