Nyiɛkpɔɔ Ŋumu, na Mbɔɔpɔ wre bijɔ wre yo na, “Pan.” A e ti ŋmba we kee ŋga loo kpan kre yo na, “Pan.” A ŋmba gbɔɔ ta, na ŋmba u chaa kre, u pan u ŋmaa nyumu kre shɔ finfin.
